That's your residence.

70
00:05:48.063 --> 00:05:50.165
I wonder why he hung up.

71
00:05:50.165 --> 00:05:53.090
Is there supposed to be someone else
there besides your wife there to answer?

72
00:05:53.090 --> 00:06:00.486
[SOUND]
>> Hello?

73
00:06:00.486 --> 00:06:02.300
>> This is United States calling.

74
00:06:02.300 --> 00:06:02.865
Are we reaching.

75
00:06:02.865 --> 00:06:06.965
[SOUND] See, he keeps hanging up.

76
